      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Class / Bridge-First Creation Flow\n\nThis graph turns the abstract authoring-ui problem into something concrete.\n\nThe goal is not perfect UI theory. The goal is one first honest creation flow that matches the post-dictionary model closely enough to build.",
