    {
      "id": "class-bridge-first-creation-flow-contextual",
      "type": "decision",
      "label": "Alternative: Contextual Plus",
      "position": {
        "x": 340,
        "y": 220
      },
      "width": 400,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "body": "Creation begins from a floating plus near the current selection or cursor.",
        "rationale": "Contextual flow:\n- click plus near a node, cluster, or cursor position\n- nearby classes and relevant bridges are offered first\n- good for locality and speed\n- weaker as a first teaching surface because the vocabulary is partially hidden until interaction\n\nBest later as an accelerator, not as the first proof.",
