    {
      "id": "class-bridge-first-creation-flow-steps",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "First Concrete Steps",
      "position": {
        "x": 1260,
        "y": 220
      },
      "width": 460,
      "height": 300,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# First Concrete Steps\n\n1. Add a `Create` tray entry point.\n2. Read node creation vocabulary from the visible bridge cluster first.\n3. Always let the legend expose `Add Markdown Node` as a courtesy default.\n4. Leave generic node creation in a lower fallback section.\n5. After generic edge draw, offer legend-visible edge classes.\n6. In selection UI, show:\n   - class source\n   - semantic meaning\n   - local overrides",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
